==Key to Hemiprocnidae== *[[#1|1]]: Two white stripes clearly present on each side of head, one going from bill to back of head and the other going from bill to neck or chest. *[[#2|2]]: Two white stripes scarcely or not present on head.
==1== *[[w:en:Hemiprocne comata|Hemiprocne comata]]: red patch present near eyes. *[[w:en:Hemiprocne mystacea|Hemiprocne mystacea]]: red patch not present near eyes.
==2== *[[w:en:Hemiprocne coronata|Hemiprocne coronata]]: Patch of reddish color present near eyes. *[[w:en:Hemiprocne longipennis|Hemiprocne longipennis]]: Patch of reddish color absent near eyes. {{BookCat}}

