{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- PLEASE ADD CATEGORIES AND INTERWIKIS AT THE BOTTOM OF THIS PAGE -->

{{tl|iszero}} returns the passed value if it evaluates as non-zero. If it is zero, by default the template returns nothing, or it can return any other value you specify. Blank inputs are treated as zeros by default, but that can be overridden.

{{tip|Non-numeric text generally will evaluate as non-zero, so you may want to pass the input value through {{tl|isnumeric}} first (see examples 12 and 14) and treat non-numeric text as a blank.}}

== Usage ==
Recognizes the following parameters
# The value to check; required
# <code>blank=</code> &mdash; To have blank values ''not'' be treated as zero, set this to any non-zero value you want returned; optional
# <code>whenzero=</code> &mdash; Set to the value you want returned if the input value evaluates to zero; optional (defaults to blank)
# <code>whenblank=</code> &mdash; Set to the value you want returned if the input value is blank; optional (defaults to blank)

== Examples ==
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero}}
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero|0}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero|0}}
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero|3}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero|3}}
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero|0|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero|0|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero||whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero||whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero||whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero|blank=1|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero||blank=1|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero||blank=1|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero||blank=1|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero|0|blank=1|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero|0|blank=1|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero|3|blank=1|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero|3|blank=1|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero|Some text|blank=1|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero|Some text|blank=1|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero|{{isnumeric|Some text}}|blank=1|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero|{{isnumeric|Some text}}|blank=¬|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero|Some text|blank=0|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero|Some text|blank=1|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}
# <code><nowiki>{{iszero|{{isnumeric|Some text}}|blank=0|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}</nowiki></code> → {{iszero|{{isnumeric|Some text}}|blank=¬|whenzero=Zero|whenblank=Blank}}

